These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, azalea
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, august, november
1. the person who growssunflower is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's birthday is in december##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Flower          | dahlia      | sunflower        | azalea     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Birthday         | december  | august      | november    |

