.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, coach, photographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, thriller
3 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, scrabble
House: gothic-revival, palace, art-deco
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the coach##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the coach is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the photographer is in an even position##4
7. the art-deco house is between the person watching disaster movies and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | coach    | photographer | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action       | thriller   |
| Game           | scrabble  | mah-jongg   | chess     |
| House         | palace | art-deco       | gothic-revival   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, tennis, sailing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, amber, ebony
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, train
1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person driving the train##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
4. the person who's sport is handball is between the person watching adventure movies and the person driving the train##2
5. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes ebony is the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Sport          | sailing | handball | tennis |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | action | adventure |
| Color           | amber       | light-blue   | ebony    |
| Transport     | train      | bike   | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, grapefruit, zucchini
House: ranch-style, palace, victorian
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, pakistani
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the palace house##3
2. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person eating zucchini is the palace house##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Hobby         | photography  | chess       | woodworking |
| Food           | zucchini     | grapefruit      | raspberry   |
| House   | palace | ranch-style | victorian     |
| Nationality   | british      | pakistani   | italian     |

