.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
House: art-deco, colonial, palace
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, manager, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, salsa, soul
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: palace-polo, volleyball, rugby
1. the manager is on the left of the person who's sport is palace-polo##1
2. the palace house is on the left of the colonial house##1
3. the bartender is in an odd position##4
4. the manager is on the left of the fan of pop##1
5. the police-officer is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
6. the police-officer is on the right of the colonial house##1
7. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| House      | palace     | colonial   | art-deco         |
| Job           | bartender | manager | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | salsa   | pop            |
| Sport   | volleyball   | rugby  | palace-polo         |

