House: wooden, craftsman, palace
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the photographer and the person who likes azure##2
2. the wooden house is the person who likes white##1
3. the person watching western movies is the craftsman house##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the social-worker##1
5. the wooden house is in an even position##4
6. the wooden house is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
