.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, white, ivory
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, lacrosse
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, metal, r&b
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, taxi
1. the person who likes fuchsia is in the middle##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
5. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the fan of ambient is between the person driving the roller and the person who likes white##2
7. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Color          | white | fuchsia | ivory |
| Sport   | cycling  | soccer    | lacrosse |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | ambient   | r&b    |
| Transport     | taxi   | car       | roller |

