.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, blue, brown
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, cucumber, garlic
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram
1. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
6. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
7. the person who likes light-blue is between the person eating cucumber and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | coffee    | soy-milk  |
| Color         | brown        | light-blue   | blue   |
| Food   | garlic       | pineapple    | cucumber |
| Transport     | tram          | quad-bike | car       |

