.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, poker
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, disco, punk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, tennis, swimming
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, lizard
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Game          | chess  | snooker   | poker      |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | punk      | blues      |
| Sport   | skiing | tennis | swimming    |
| Pet           | lizard   | horse     | chinchilla |

