3. the teacher is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the thai##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the dancer is in an odd position##4
7. the dancer is on the left or right of the teacher##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
