.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, boat, airplane
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, horror
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, horse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, davidoff, baccarat
1. the baccarat-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
7. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Transport      | airplane       | boat   | train |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | disaster |
| Pet           | bird      | chinchilla | horse    |
| Cigar         | davidoff  | baccarat     | fonseca |

