3 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, parkour
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, poppy, rose
1. the accountant is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the accountant is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the analyst is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who growsrose##1
6. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
7. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
9. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | accountant | analyst   | fisherman |
| Pet   | bird  | mouse    | goat    |
| Sport         | cricket    | badminton | parkour   |
| Flower     | poppy  | rose     | iris  |

