4. the owner of the turtle is between the police-officer and the fan of techno##2
5. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
6. the argentine is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Music-Genre         | folk    | r&b   | techno      |
