3. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
4. the person who growspoppy is the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
7. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
8. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Food          | peas     | pear   | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | epic   | drama      |
| Color   | pink | coral | brown    |
| Flower     | poppy  | tulip   | iris |

