3 different games are played: whist, go, billiard
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, dutch, pakistani
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, skateboarding
1. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating nectarine and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing go##1
6. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Food          | onion     | cauliflower | nectarine   |
| Game         | billiard   | whist | go |
| Nationality   | pakistani | dutch       | colombian   |
| Sport     | skateboarding     | biathlon  | rugby        |

