2. the mexican is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is the person who growstulip##1
5. the pakistani is in an even position##4
6. the fan of house is the mexican##1
7. the french is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who growszinnia is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Flower          | zinnia  | orchid   | tulip |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | punk      | house   |
| Nationality   | french     | pakistani | mexican |
| Movie-Genre         | time-travel | drama   | documentary   |

