1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the chinese is on the left of the musician##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the police-officer is on the left or right of the dancer##3
6. the police-officer is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Job           | dancer  | police-officer | musician   |
| Nationality   | japanese | chinese           | canadian      |
| Pet           | mouse   | horse          | guinea-pig |
| House     | art-deco    | cape-cod           | victorian |

 